Titolo: Bound by Flame

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: Bound by Flame is a fantasy-themed action role-playing game that was released on 9 May 2014. Bound by Flame puts the player in the role of a victim of demonic possession, where it is necessary to choose between the evil powers that are offered or rejecting them in favor of developing heroic talents.

Genere: Action role-playing 

Valutazione: 55
